#How to install Mord package for anaconda-spyder users

Go to the site : https://pypi.python.org/pypi/mord/0.4
download the latest mord package file and unzip the file
open the anaconda command prompt(or gitcmd)and enter:
pip install mord
Close the spyder and reopen
check the installation by typing the below code in spyder:
import mord as m